results.name: First difference sequence of A002202. Difference between consecutive possible values for phi(n).
link: Reinhard Zumkeller, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000
example: 12 and 16 are the 7th and 8th possible totient values 12 = phi(13), 16 = phi(17),
while {13,14,15} are impossible ones; thus 16 - 12 = 4 = a(7) = A002202(8) - A002202(7).
